[/quote]Never subsurfed, lol, Blender doesn’t have subsurf, at least i don’t think, I just turned up gloss and fixed up faces.

[/quote]Kewl, btw i found a beastly rendering utility, its called Yafaray.[/quote]
Yeah, there’s many rendering utilities. I just use a built in option called “Ambient Occlusion” which, for most low-poly models, provides high enough quality results.
